Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.18,0:28:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetime. And in this lifetime, by God, they
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.18,0:28:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,step over every ant until they get it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.33,0:28:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they do about the flies?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.24,0:28:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. After many years
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.20,0:28:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I had an office in New York, you know, very
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.20,0:28:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,famous office. And behind the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.54,0:28:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,drapes I had hidden a butterfly net.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.54,0:28:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And when the patients weren't there,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.54,0:28:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,there was always some flies flying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.57,0:28:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hid this butterfly net behind the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.57,0:28:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,drapes. And when the staff wasn't there
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.57,0:28:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and no patients were there, I quickly ran out and
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.57,0:28:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,snared them and put them out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.57,0:28:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was a
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.57,0:28:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,strict Buddhist for a long time. I didn't eat
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.57,0:28:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,meat, I was a vegetarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.94,0:28:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No sugar, no, I didn't kill even a fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.94,0:29:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought they would all think
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.28,0:29:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a little weird, so I kept it hidden behind
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.28,0:29:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the drapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.76,0:29:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The patient walks out and the doctor runs
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.76,0:29:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,around with a butterfly net.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.63,0:29:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He opens the window, puts them out,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.63,0:29:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,blesses them, bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.63,0:29:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.63,0:29:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was a
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.92,0:29:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,secret Buddhist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.92,0:29:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the first Zen Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.91,0:29:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,in New York City. I was a secret Buddhist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.91,0:29:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it was
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.23,0:29:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.23,0:29:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,pop culture for a while, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.23,0:29:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I secretly saved
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.23,0:29:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the life of the flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.53,0:29:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we? Oh, Islam.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.73,0:29:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, we had Islam.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.73,0:29:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Islam, the Koran, is still at
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.73,0:29:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,700. The Koran, I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.33,0:29:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth of the Koran then, has been
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.33,0:29:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,savaged
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.43,0:29:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,by the political
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.72,0:29:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,people, which as
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.72,0:30:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Christianity was at the time of the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.72,0:30:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Inquisition, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.91,0:30:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So any political group can come in
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.91,0:30:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and claim that it is part of a
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.91,0:30:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,religious thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.80,0:30:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ayatollah in Iran,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.80,0:30:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,however, it's extremely low, as do all the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.80,0:30:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,mullahs and the rest of the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.94,0:30:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Arabic world. But
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.94,0:30:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth of the basic religion itself
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.94,0:30:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is at 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.41,0:30:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Islam, 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.41,0:30:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Islam, as practiced, is 325.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.41,0:30:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Muslims,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.24,0:30:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,205.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.58,0:30:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Modern Judaism, I'm not all that much
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.58,0:30:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of an expert on Judaism
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.58,0:30:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and its history.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.75,0:30:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I know there's several main schools,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.75,0:30:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,conservatives and modern
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.75,0:30:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and traditional, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.32,0:30:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So that would require somebody who knows
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.32,0:30:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,something about it to set up what should be
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.32,0:30:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated. I don't myself know that much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.32,0:30:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinto itself is
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.42,0:30:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,350. And of course
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.83,0:30:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that played a big part in World War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.83,0:31:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way of the Dao
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.22,0:31:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.08,0:31:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, relax into the flow,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.08,0:31:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the realization of that which you already
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.08,0:31:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,are. That's the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.38,0:31:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,way of the Dao.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.66,0:31:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,590? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.74,0:31:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That phrase, relax into the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.19,0:31:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,reality of that which you already are.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.19,0:31:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates over 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.30,0:31:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 590.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.30,0:31:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax into the reality of that which you already are.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.30,0:31:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates over 595.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.30,0:31:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,600.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.04,0:31:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.25,0:31:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right at 600. So that would be
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.25,0:31:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,an expression
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.35,0:31:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of Daoism.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.35,0:31:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's spelled T-A-O, but it's
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.35,0:31:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,pronounced Dao.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.65,0:31:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Comparative calibrations. We said
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.94,0:31:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,these are all things people have sent us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.94,0:32:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have stacks
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.05,0:32:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of them to go. We're going to be old and gray
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.05,0:32:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,by the time we finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.05,0:32:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And the book's going to be this thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.05,0:32:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,People keep sending us more.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.05,0:32:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep sending us more books. Every day in the mail
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.05,0:32:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,there's more books. Please calibrate this, calibrate this teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.05,0:32:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so we got some of
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.28,0:32:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the evidence. What have they got? I don't know the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.28,0:32:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,reason for all these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.76,0:32:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But these are the calibrations
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.76,0:32:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,which we got, and we've
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.76,0:32:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of course
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.76,0:32:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,reverified these
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.25,0:32:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,before we made them into a slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.25,0:32:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday we went back
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.25,0:32:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,over each one of them, because I don't want
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.25,0:32:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,them to be there and be an error.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.25,0:32:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We said that these are
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.27,0:32:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,accurate as they stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.27,0:32:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.92,0:32:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of this group over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.69,0:32:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This slide is accurate as it stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.00,0:32:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This slide is accurate
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.13,0:32:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,as it stands, as much as we know
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.13,0:32:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.42,0:32:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Any one of these can make a shift
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.42,0:32:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in tomorrow, just like doing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.42,0:33:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the giant corporations. The minute they
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.42,0:33:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,fire that CEO, the calibration level
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.42,0:33:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of that corporation jumps up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.64,0:33:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We've also done
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.64,0:33:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,100 corporations.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.64,0:33:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been busy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.64,0:33:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did all the countries in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.64,0:33:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,did all the spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.64,0:33:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,teachers, all the books, and
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.64,0:33:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we were working on the Fortune 500
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.64,0:33:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,list of the best, biggest
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.64,0:33:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,corporations in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.05,0:33:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.05,0:33:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,this is part of the ongoing study.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.05,0:33:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the Institute for Advanced
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.05,0:33:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Theoretical Research, Consciousness Research.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.05,0:33:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So they say, what do you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.11,0:33:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,do there? Well, this is what we do. We try to find
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.11,0:33:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,out what is the reality of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.25,0:33:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it totally changes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.25,0:33:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,your conception of it, your understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.25,0:33:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,of it. It's like a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.70,0:33:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,two-dimensional world now suddenly becoming
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.70,0:33:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,three-dimensional and technicolor. It takes on
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.70,0:33:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole different significance and
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.70,0:33:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.65,0:33:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventh-day Adventists, I don't know what their
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.65,0:33:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,problem is.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.65,0:34:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.64,0:34:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of these get caught up in
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.64,0:34:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what it is. A lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.64,0:34:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,these groups get caught up in the Book of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.64,0:34:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Revelations. And you remember
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.73,0:34:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the Book of Revelations calibrates at 70.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.73,0:34:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventy, in contrast
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.86,0:34:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to the New Testament.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.44,0:34:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you get caught up, and it's easy to get
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.44,0:34:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,caught up in the Book of Revelations because it's
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.44,0:34:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so dramatic. I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.23,0:34:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, drama tends to
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.23,0:34:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,suck people right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.23,0:34:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds so dramatic that it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.23,0:34:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.23,0:34:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.28,0:34:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.71,0:34:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She interrupted. How do you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.59,0:34:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you asking something?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.26,0:34:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know what time it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.05,0:35:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it three minutes to twelve?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.61,0:35:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it can't be three minutes to twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.61,0:35:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We just started. It's only 830, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.61,0:35:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we've got three minutes to finish
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.05,0:35:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the rest of these religions, and then we'll break for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.05,0:35:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's no clock in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.86,0:35:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be we're living in
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.34,0:35:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,timelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.40,0:35:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We disappeared time this morning. I don't know where time went.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.40,0:35:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice it. Did you notice that? I didn't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.40,0:35:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we'll quickly run through all these.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.40,0:35:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them are sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.40,0:35:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,fun to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.69,0:35:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Jehovah's Witness 195, they have sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.69,0:35:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a strange
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.69,0:35:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding of the Old Testament with sort of a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.69,0:35:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,thing about
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.36,0:35:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what's expected there. I forget what they call that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.36,0:35:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so right-wing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.51,0:35:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,fundamentalist Christian and right-wing all
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.51,0:35:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that tends to come down quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.51,0:35:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Urantia book is 150.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.51,0:35:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wicca, as you would expect, is 160.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.51,0:35:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Army of God is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.61,0:35:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the people that blow up
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.61,0:35:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,abortion
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.63,0:36:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,clinics and kill
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.63,0:36:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,gynecologists and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.63,0:36:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine running around with a bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.32,0:36:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can't find an abortion clinic to blow
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.32,0:36:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.09,0:36:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to say you're a
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.92,0:36:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,terrorist and you can't find a busload of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.92,0:36:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,children to blow up. Imagine the frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.92,0:36:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got these bombs and you can't find a busload of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.92,0:36:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,kids. Okay, so
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.53,0:36:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Army...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.01,0:36:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,New Age gets sort of out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.01,0:36:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They recently
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.01,0:36:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,had a
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.01,0:36:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,fairy festival here and it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.01,0:36:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated at 140.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.28,0:36:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.90,0:36:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,these are sort of primitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.19,0:36:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,New Ageism itself, which we
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.19,0:36:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,said is one of the things you can get
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.19,0:36:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled into.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.71,0:36:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Practically all of us here at one time, I'm sure, have had a
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.71,0:37:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,psychic reading. We've done the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.71,0:37:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,tarot cards. I mean, everybody's got to check
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.71,0:37:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it out, do the I Ching, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.86,0:37:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you find out what that's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.86,0:37:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's part of curiosity. It's part of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.86,0:37:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.86,0:37:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's out there? What are the alternatives?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.86,0:37:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it look like? A lot of it is
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.86,0:37:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,attractive. And I'll tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.26,0:37:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what tends to calibrate quite low,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.26,0:37:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,disappointingly low. We notice
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.38,0:37:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,characteristically there'll be at least a quarter
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.38,0:37:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,page in the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.73,0:37:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And it always has a Christ-like
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.73,0:37:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,figure there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.05,0:37:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who comes from a long
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.13,0:37:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual tradition of the sixth
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.13,0:37:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,reincarnation of the ancient something.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.13,0:37:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's going to give you a four or five day
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.13,0:37:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,workshop on how to breathe your way to God
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.13,0:37:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is going to cost you 500 bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.13,0:37:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've noticed that there's a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.38,0:37:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,seduction to it. He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.55,0:37:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what's characteristic? Because there's a whole lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.55,0:37:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,East Indian gurus that have come down a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.55,0:37:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,long way. I mean a long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.55,0:37:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,From mid to high 500s down
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.80,0:38:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,less than 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.01,0:38:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Characteristic of those groups is
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.01,0:38:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the glamour
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.01,0:38:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of spiritual seduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.84,0:38:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The mystical, magical,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.15,0:38:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and on the internet it tells you they are the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.15,0:38:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,great savior, the new avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.15,0:38:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And you calibrate them
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.28,0:38:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're 290.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.11,0:38:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So mankind projects
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.11,0:38:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,onto them their own
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.11,0:38:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,fantasies and wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.11,0:38:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is garbed and robed
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.15,0:38:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in seductiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.15,0:38:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,once you be
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.38,0:38:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a watchful eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.57,0:38:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's trying to pull you into the glamour.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.57,0:38:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So the glamourization of spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.57,0:38:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,reality with sandals,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.57,0:38:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,incense, bald heads, flowing robes
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.57,0:38:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and showing peculiar things
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.57,0:38:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and sitting cross legged and smoking weird
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.57,0:39:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,things and being feeble at the same
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.57,0:39:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,time is not necessarily
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.21,0:39:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the greatest
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.61,0:39:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,truth on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.59,0:39:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But the oohs and the ahhs.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.59,0:39:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look we've all been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.59,0:39:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So and so's ashram and walked through
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.59,0:39:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the incense and all the praying
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.59,0:39:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and the old headed people and
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.94,0:39:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the weird crap you eat with two fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.94,0:39:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Disgusting. I knew I wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.94,0:39:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,going to be a Hare Krishna right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.94,0:39:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is strained
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.44,0:39:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,peas and you eat it with two fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.44,0:39:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.53,0:39:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to God is not
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.46,0:39:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,through colonic irrigations
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.46,0:39:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.53,0:39:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,strained peas.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.53,0:39:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll prove that later
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.26,0:39:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,on because I think we did strain peas
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.26,0:39:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in colonic irrigations. I think it comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.26,0:39:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright so
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.09,0:39:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,what's wrong with this is
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.09,0:40:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it's adolescent fantasying.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.09,0:40:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the child, the spiritual child
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.09,0:40:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,who's enamored
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.09,0:40:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of the flowers and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.09,0:40:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the fairy dances around the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.23,0:40:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,maypole. Alright so now
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.42,0:40:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we can see what these all are
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.42,0:40:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and we notice that cults can
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.42,0:40:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,go anywhere from 50 to
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.42,0:40:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,160 and we've already
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.98,0:40:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,described cults.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.50,0:40:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A cult has
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.50,0:40:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,membership. You have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.50,0:40:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,certain things. You have to pay certain things.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.50,0:40:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher, the head
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.30,0:40:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,person has all kinds of privileges
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.30,0:40:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.71,0:40:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They can have sex but you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.71,0:40:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You should turn over your money to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.73,0:40:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the whole charisma
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.13,0:40:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of the cult is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.13,0:40:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so well known now. I think several
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.13,0:40:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of them having fallen in the last 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.13,0:40:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with a loud crash
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.32,0:40:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,many people are quite aware of what a
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.32,0:40:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,cult looks like and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.32,0:40:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,sounds like. The accumulation
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.63,0:40:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of wealth and the attraction seems
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.63,0:41:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to be of those gurus who fall
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.63,0:41:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,into power over others.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.76,0:41:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.76,0:41:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the term guru itself
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.76,0:41:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and the term baba.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.90,0:41:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We found that both of them make you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.90,0:41:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The term guru
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.15,0:41:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,started to make you go weak after 1960.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.15,0:41:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.15,0:41:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,traditionally it was
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.15,0:41:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a title of honor for a
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.69,0:41:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.69,0:41:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,who calibrated. We said we found out
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.69,0:41:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it was 540 or 460.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.69,0:41:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,True guru
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.69,0:41:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,was 540 or 560.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.21,0:41:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We got in these books
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.21,0:41:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,not to use the term
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.26,0:41:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because I go over every page I've written
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.26,0:41:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and I say there's something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.26,0:41:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We always get the word guru is not correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.26,0:41:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to use it in its historic
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.26,0:41:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,classical meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.46,0:41:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was advised not to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.46,0:41:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Also the word baba.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.46,0:41:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.50,0:41:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we asked what was it in 1960?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.50,0:41:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The word guru fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.69,0:42:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The word guru fell
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.69,0:42:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in 1960.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.69,0:42:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The influence of the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.55,0:42:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,glamorization through the media
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.55,0:42:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and the exploitation
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.55,0:42:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,somehow brought down
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.55,0:42:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the calibrated energy of that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.55,0:42:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,title.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.15,0:42:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we have other things
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.15,0:42:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.15,0:42:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,These seem to have to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.15,0:42:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,control of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.57,0:42:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Those which
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.17,0:42:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,have fallen off and become cults
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.17,0:42:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,seem to have to do with controlling people,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.17,0:42:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,having lots of followers
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.44,0:42:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and interfering with their personal
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.44,0:42:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.01,0:42:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine a real teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.30,0:42:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,really caring whether you stay married
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.30,0:42:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or don't get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.30,0:42:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What would he care about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.30,0:42:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you sell your oxen
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.30,0:42:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and you don't sell your oxen
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.30,0:42:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,or whether you eat soup for lunch
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.34,0:42:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,or you eat fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.34,0:42:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would a person want to control you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.34,0:42:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A true teacher has no interest in controlling people
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.34,0:43:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and having followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.34,0:43:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants troops and zillions of people following you around
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.34,0:43:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're a real nuisance?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.34,0:43:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Throwing melons at you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.34,0:43:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.50,0:43:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodging flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.50,0:43:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.50,0:43:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.50,0:43:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Qigong, Shiite Muslim cults.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.50,0:43:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stop at the end of this list
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.50,0:43:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and break for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.50,0:43:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is of course the cult that set off
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.50,0:43:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the poison bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.50,0:43:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Tokyo subway.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.59,0:43:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All these things that are done
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.59,0:43:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.75,0:43:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget which one this one is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.75,0:43:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fellow
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.88,0:43:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,who recently was in the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.88,0:43:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.88,0:43:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,he only calibrates to 130.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.23,0:43:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one the salvation of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.23,0:43:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to come by an extraterrestrial,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.23,0:43:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.23,0:43:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.94,0:43:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Dr. Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.00,0:43:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We see what the Catholic
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.00,0:43:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,religion itself stands at.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.00,0:43:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It still stands solid and firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.00,0:44:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But its positionality
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.13,0:44:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,on pedophilia
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.13,0:44:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is frankly at 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.13,0:44:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.63,0:44:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,even though one is a great world leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.63,0:44:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we know from past presidents and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.63,0:44:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you can still have errors
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.69,0:44:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.69,0:44:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently it did not bring down the church itself
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.69,0:44:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,because the church as such,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.69,0:44:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,as a body of traditional
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.05,0:44:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.05,0:44:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,stands firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.05,0:44:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But the decision itself
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.28,0:44:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,has not had a good effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.50,0:44:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.92,0:44:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we know that it's bad to be judgmental.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.03,0:44:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.23,0:44:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you can tell that...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.36,0:44:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.36,0:44:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we had one more to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.36,0:44:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.36,0:44:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this one we've hit before.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.36,0:45:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow the Old Testament,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.57,0:45:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the book of Revelations we know,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.57,0:45:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and we know that the calibration of,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.57,0:45:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,which we'll get to in the next slide,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.57,0:45:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.57,0:45:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of Scriptures has to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.05,0:45:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,whether or not you have
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.05,0:45:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Old Testament certain books.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.05,0:45:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And the minute you take them out,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.05,0:45:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the calibrated level of the Bible jumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.57,0:45:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's down three, four hundred points.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.57,0:45:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you remove those books
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.57,0:45:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that make you go weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.57,0:45:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,especially the book of Revelations,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.57,0:45:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the calibrated level.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.57,0:45:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the Lamsa Bible minus the Old Testament
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.57,0:45:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,with the exception of Psalms,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.69,0:45:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Proverbs, and Genesis,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.30,0:45:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Lamsa version,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.30,0:45:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,which is from the Aramaic
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.17,0:45:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than the Greek,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.44,0:45:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 880,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.44,0:45:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,which is quite a bit different
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.94,0:45:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,than that translated from the Greek
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.94,0:45:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of common English translation, which is only 480.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.05,0:45:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.38,0:46:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to be able to calibrate the level of truth of things
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.38,0:46:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is of great,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.38,0:46:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is a great advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.38,0:46:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget we're at the leading edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.38,0:46:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Man never had this tool before.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.42,0:46:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fault people for going in the wrong direction
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.42,0:46:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,if they've got no compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.48,0:46:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night we watched two guys who get lost
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.48,0:46:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,up in the Rockies at the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.48,0:46:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Continental Divide,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.51,0:46:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.51,0:46:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,this guy's out there without even a compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.51,0:46:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And his buddy goes a mile ahead of him
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.51,0:46:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in the strand zone. I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.51,0:46:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,he goes a mile ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.51,0:46:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in the snowstorm,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.51,0:46:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and strains his buddy a mile behind him
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.51,0:46:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,who doesn't have a compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.51,0:46:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever wandered around the Continental Divide,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.51,0:46:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what it's like in the middle of winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.51,0:46:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember the Continental Divide
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.05,0:46:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,on the 4th of July, it was snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.05,0:46:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I marked that in my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.30,0:46:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, remember this, on the 4th of July,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.30,0:46:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the Continental Divide, it was snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.30,0:46:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so it's time to take
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.86,0:46:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a break for lunch. Has everybody been able
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.86,0:46:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to handle this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.07,0:46:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't want to upset anybody, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.07,0:47:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned my co-dependency
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.92,0:47:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,over to God, and it's your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.25,0:47:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're on the air, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.03,0:47:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We have
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.03,0:47:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,21 pages of calibrations,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.23,0:47:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,each of which has 30
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.23,0:47:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrations on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.23,0:47:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.03,0:47:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonya? Sonya is the one responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.03,0:47:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for having it in the form
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.03,0:47:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that we could actually project it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.03,0:47:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for the audience. She worked around the clock
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.03,0:47:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.57,0:47:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,21 pages with 30 calibrations
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.57,0:47:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,on each one was quite a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.40,0:47:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of effort to get it done for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.40,0:47:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So we want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.46,0:47:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dedication.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.46,0:47:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dedication.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.46,0:48:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.90,0:48:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were doing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.90,0:48:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,higher spiritual groups, I thought I'd mention
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.90,0:48:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that the Bee Gees calibrated 510.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.90,0:48:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought you'd like to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.82,0:48:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it, I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.98,0:48:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, because I'm trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.28,0:48:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,talk about what is a spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.28,0:48:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, a pious sounding
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.28,0:48:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,hymn, you might say, oh, that's so
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.28,0:48:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,pious and Lord Jesus this and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.28,0:48:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd say, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.34,0:48:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the Bee Gees are at 510.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.34,0:48:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that? Well, when you hear the Bee
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.86,0:48:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gees, it's hard to sit still, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.86,0:48:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's almost impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.92,0:48:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,not to dance at 510
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.92,0:48:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.21,0:48:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because it brings up the joy of your
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.21,0:48:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,own existence, you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.21,0:48:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ecstatically joyful
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.21,0:48:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.23,0:48:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's the reality we're looking
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.23,0:48:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,for. Not which is
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.65,0:48:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,pain and sin and suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.65,0:48:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and chains and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.65,0:48:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But that which leads to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.92,0:49:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,truth, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.46,0:49:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because you start experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.46,0:49:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,moments of joy
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.46,0:49:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're like
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.59,0:49:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,outside of time and you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.94,0:49:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,know you're on the right way. And then
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.94,0:49:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,they disappear. In the beginning they appear
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.94,0:49:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.94,0:49:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't feel bad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.94,0:49:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't feel bad about it. I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.94,0:49:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,not feel bad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.17,0:49:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You let go of that little
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.44,0:49:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,piece of karma and now you've got some more. Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.44,0:49:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But those
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.40,0:49:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,little glimpses that you begin to get
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.40,0:49:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,early in the, early
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.59,0:49:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, tell you that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.82,0:49:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you're on the right road.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.82,0:49:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What we're talking
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.05,0:49:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,about of course are
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.05,0:49:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,first of all things that are outside of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.05,0:49:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,time, things
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.44,0:49:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of recent discovery
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.44,0:49:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,together with the subjective
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.88,0:49:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,experiential which is totally outside
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.88,0:50:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of time. The field of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.90,0:50:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the nature of the field of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.00,0:50:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness is that it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.00,0:50:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,registers everything and anything
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.00,0:50:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that happened, every event,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.67,0:50:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,every thought, every feeling, every incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.67,0:50:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing escapes the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.67,0:50:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,field of consciousness. Consequently,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.25,0:50:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that which has
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.71,0:50:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,preceded us in time is registered
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.71,0:50:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,forever. It says
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.88,0:50:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in scripture, not one hair of your
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.88,0:50:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,head shall go uncounted and that is a
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.88,0:50:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,fact. It's registered
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.88,0:50:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,there forever. It's obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.23,0:50:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,then that you can't
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.38,0:50:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,use kinesiology about the future
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.38,0:50:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because it has no reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.38,0:50:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a hypothetical possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.73,0:50:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and because it hasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.19,0:50:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,been printed out yet, there's no way to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.19,0:50:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,get that newspaper. You can't get it in
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.19,0:50:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,tomorrow's newspaper today because
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.69,0:51:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it has not unfolded. So
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.69,0:51:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in a way what consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.82,0:51:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is, is a recording of the history
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.82,0:51:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of evolution, of
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.92,0:51:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,creation. It's the history of
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.92,0:51:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,creation as it appears
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.98,0:51:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,as evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.09,0:51:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and the appearance in evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.09,0:51:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of course is to perception
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.11,0:51:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and beyond perception there's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.11,0:51:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,evolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.11,0:51:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.44,0:51:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,need explanation at all
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.44,0:51:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's only a way of looking
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.44,0:51:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,at things. So let's
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.78,0:51:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,go on to the next exciting chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.78,0:51:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how far we'll get through it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.26,0:51:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.26,0:51:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,any one of these calibrations
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.26,0:51:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,could, you could spend a whole
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.26,0:51:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,couple years studying it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.26,0:51:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to get the complete story. What happened
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.26,0:51:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,at the Council of Nicaea,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.26,0:51:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,why various things calibrated what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.26,0:51:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.30,0:51:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole world of study in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.30,0:51:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're sort of like Galileo
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.30,0:51:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,who discovered the telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.30,0:52:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and now he's going to give you the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.30,0:52:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,rudiments of the heavens
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.32,0:52:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but astronomy is
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.32,0:52:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,around the clock by thousands of people with
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.32,0:52:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,computers and they're still discovering
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.32,0:52:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,things. So that's where we're at in the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.32,0:52:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,unfolding of this sort of field
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.32,0:52:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of conscious awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.32,0:52:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that is of such recent
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.32,0:52:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,origin. However it was
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.48,0:52:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,predicted and it did
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.78,0:52:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,come into existence
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.78,0:52:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,subsequent to the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.78,0:52:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,jump in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.36,0:52:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of mankind from 190 to 207
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.36,0:52:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which happened in the late
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.36,0:52:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,1980s. So
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.98,0:52:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,all of it seems to
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.30,0:52:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,coincide and everything as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.30,0:52:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,see happens in
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.30,0:52:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,absolute perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.30,0:52:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't really need you in a way
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.84,0:52:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.05,0:52:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is evolutionary
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.05,0:52:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,unfoldment then
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.05,0:52:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is what we witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.13,0:52:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So we tracked down
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.13,0:53:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as I say we have
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.30,0:53:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,quite a few major subjects. Spirituality
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.30,0:53:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of them. Americana is another.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.30,0:53:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,History, archaeology, paleontology,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.30,0:53:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,art, science,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.50,0:53:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,philosophy. All
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.50,0:53:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of them are things we are working on currently.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.50,0:53:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But this one is at least
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.69,0:53:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,type Delphic dissonia and
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.69,0:53:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so we have spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.69,0:53:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,titles you see because
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.69,0:53:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout the years various titles are
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.69,0:53:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,used by various spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.69,0:53:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,groups and organizations and just
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.69,0:53:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,what does that mean you know see.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.98,0:53:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A true master is 700
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.98,0:53:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and over. A saint is 700 and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.98,0:53:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord is a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.98,0:53:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A sage is 700 and
