Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.94,1:09:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the lower
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.39,1:09:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of consciousness, the more you think you are
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.39,1:09:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that and therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.56,1:09:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,there's considerable grief.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.56,1:10:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mourning the loss of the physicality
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.56,1:10:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and the life that went with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.56,1:10:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As you're more advanced, you're very happy to be
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.56,1:10:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,rid of it and you could probably be
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.56,1:10:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,cremated in 10-20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.56,1:10:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You go,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.56,1:10:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,whew,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.56,1:10:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,what a relief.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.68,1:10:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like taking off all this baggage and weight.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.68,1:10:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like all your clothes are so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.68,1:10:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You take them all off.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.68,1:10:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You take this helmet off.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.68,1:10:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You take all this crap off and now you feel light and free.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.68,1:10:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see any point in
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.93,1:10:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,mourning it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.09,1:10:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what it says
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.09,1:10:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,as a generality. Wait three days.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.09,1:10:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We asked, can a human actually live
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.25,1:10:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,on prana energy and we got true.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.25,1:10:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That is so.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.38,1:10:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a fabled saint who lived her life
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.38,1:10:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in Germany
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.38,1:10:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,solely on prana.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.89,1:10:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.97,1:10:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so doubtful about that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.55,1:10:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.71,1:10:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She's of course fabled
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.71,1:11:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,as a great saint.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.06,1:11:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness level is already set at birth.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.06,1:11:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already mentioned that is true.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.06,1:11:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The exact time of death
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.06,1:11:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving the physical body is karmically
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.06,1:11:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,set at birth. That is true.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.06,1:11:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Comparative calibrations.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.75,1:11:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghosts are real.
