Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.93,1:11:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Haunting. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.93,1:11:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The prophecy at end times upon which
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.93,1:11:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of people make a lot of
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.26,1:11:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,gain of
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.26,1:11:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,pulling off the fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.64,1:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Prophecy at end times are nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.64,1:11:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Including Saint Matthew's
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.38,1:11:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,prophecy at end times. His is nonsense too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.38,1:11:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One can experience
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.55,1:11:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,one's own physical death.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.55,1:11:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not possible.
