Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.02,1:11:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't experience what goes on with the carpet
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.67,1:12:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm not a carpet.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.67,1:12:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When I thought I was a carpet
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.67,1:12:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were walking on me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.31,1:12:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go on to the next
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.31,1:12:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,exciting chapter.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.72,1:12:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you how much time
