Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.72,1:12:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The correcting of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.72,1:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The inquisition of
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.72,1:12:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the great fable of the inquisition
