Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.97,1:26:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.97,1:26:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Constitution of the United States
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.97,1:26:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is partly the result
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.97,1:26:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Native Americans,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.97,1:26:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why I honor them.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.19,1:26:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmapa, 630.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.19,1:26:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Makananda, who I got to meet,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.19,1:26:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,he was great fun,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.26,1:26:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and he used to take these orange
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.26,1:26:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,knit caps off and throw them
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.26,1:26:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,into the audience,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.26,1:26:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and people wanted his energy
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.26,1:26:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to run and get these orange
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.46,1:26:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,knit caps and pull them on.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.46,1:26:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Makananda was self,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.18,1:26:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the realization of the self.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.18,1:26:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Vivekananda, 610.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.22,1:26:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,620.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.85,1:26:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the great mystics
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.85,1:26:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in Hebrew tradition,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.85,1:27:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Rabbi Moses de Leon of Granada,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.85,1:27:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,who was 14th century,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.85,1:27:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,was at 720.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.69,1:27:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisargadatta and Ramana Maharshi
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.69,1:27:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,were at 720.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.69,1:27:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramesh Bolsikar,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.61,1:27:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,who I spent seven days with,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.61,1:27:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,came out, yes, he was at 760.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.61,1:27:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a translator
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.85,1:27:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,for Nisargadatta
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.09,1:27:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,for some 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.09,1:27:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and he himself became enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.78,1:27:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to spend some time with him
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.78,1:27:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in 20 palms, or whatever it's called
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.78,1:27:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in California.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.97,1:27:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Confucius at 590.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.97,1:27:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Patrick, 590.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.46,1:27:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wallace Black Elk of Lakota, 499.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.46,1:27:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,John Calvin, 580.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.68,1:27:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,John Wesley, 360.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.68,1:27:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Martin Luther, 580.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.68,1:27:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The current Dalai Lama, 570.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.68,1:27:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maharishi, Transcendental Meditation, 410.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.68,1:27:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Swami Ram Dass,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.68,1:27:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,who died in 63, 570.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.68,1:27:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert Powell,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.68,1:27:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,more a contemporary,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.68,1:28:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,whose books are available
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.68,1:28:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,via Dove Press, 525.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.68,1:28:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Joel Golson at 455.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.68,1:28:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Poonjanand, HWL,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.81,1:28:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,which I think is a cool name,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.81,1:28:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,370.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.68,1:28:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a lot of Rinpoches,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.68,1:28:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of Rinpoches,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.89,1:28:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and this one's 499,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.89,1:28:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and Tibetan Buddhist.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.89,1:28:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Any questions about what we've covered so far?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.89,1:28:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the answers
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.71,1:28:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we've gotten when we asked the question,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.71,1:28:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way we ask the question
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.71,1:28:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is just the way we do
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.71,1:28:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in the audience this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.73,1:28:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You sort of intuit,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.73,1:28:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and the more you do this, the closer you get.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.73,1:28:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we were doing countries, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.73,1:28:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we began to suspect that there was
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.73,1:28:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,something wrong with our technique.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.77,1:28:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'd say,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.77,1:28:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Banja Waja, and I'd say
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.77,1:28:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it's over 460, 465.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.77,1:28:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We hit it within five points every time.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.77,1:28:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say, how can that be?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.77,1:28:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try Gunga Bongo,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.77,1:29:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd say let's start at 210, 215.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.77,1:29:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We would almost know where to start,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.77,1:29:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,because otherwise you're going to spend half an hour
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.77,1:29:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,summing up the whole scale of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.77,1:29:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can intuit pretty much
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.77,1:29:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,almost where to start.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.02,1:29:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And the more you do it,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.02,1:29:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you get very, very close.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.02,1:29:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And if one of you doesn't get the question,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.02,1:29:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the other one will intuit it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.73,1:29:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So it can become extremely fast
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.73,1:29:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and extremely accurate once you get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.96,1:29:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now we have other
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.96,1:29:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibetan Buddhists,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.11,1:29:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.76,1:29:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that was the next one,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.94,1:29:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the second one was the first guy
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.94,1:29:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to scale Mount Everest.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.46,1:29:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.97,1:29:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu, Wu Wei, 475.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.31,1:29:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dayananda Swami, 460.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.31,1:29:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Charles Fillmore, 45.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.31,1:29:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The founder,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.97,1:29:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,supposed founder of
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.97,1:29:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibetan Buddhism,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.97,1:29:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,which I don't actually believe the collaboration,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.05,1:29:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but because the history of
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.05,1:30:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,ancient teachings is muddled,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.05,1:30:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Padmasambhava,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.05,1:30:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,founder,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.21,1:30:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and the term Babaji,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.21,1:30:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this is also bandied around.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.21,1:30:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's all kinds of entities called Babaji.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.21,1:30:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.27,1:30:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to find out what that really is,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.27,1:30:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd have to spend some time and some research.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.27,1:30:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Which Babaji are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.27,1:30:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently alive,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.56,1:30:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of legend,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.56,1:30:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.93,1:30:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramchandra.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.93,1:30:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Swami Satchinananda,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.93,1:30:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,who we all liked,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.93,1:30:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,was 605.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.93,1:30:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He had such a great beard, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.93,1:30:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Meher Baba, 240.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.93,1:30:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Karuna Maya, 220.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.93,1:30:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Garchin Rinpoche, 385.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.93,1:30:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,460.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.32,1:30:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Old Testament prophets were not
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.32,1:30:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,what I would expect they would be.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.61,1:30:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,202.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.61,1:30:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenzin Gyaltsen,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.61,1:30:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't that the guy that climbed the Himalayas?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.61,1:30:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.73,1:30:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the wrong Tenzin.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.73,1:31:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenzin Gyaltsen, correct,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.73,1:31:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is 599.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.73,1:31:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a very advanced entity, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.02,1:31:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And he climbed, he was the first.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.82,1:31:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.82,1:31:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice Bailey, 445.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.82,1:31:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't really a channel.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.85,1:31:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She's more,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.85,1:31:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,channeling is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.34,1:31:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She's more an intermediary,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.34,1:31:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,much like Helen
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.34,1:31:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,who did the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.50,1:31:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen didn't hear anybody
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.50,1:31:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,speaking to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.50,1:31:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like she heard an entity there
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.50,1:31:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,speaking to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.94,1:31:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She called it inner dictation.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.94,1:31:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like an inner knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.94,1:31:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,unfolded itself from within her mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.07,1:31:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence by sentence,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.07,1:31:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and she just typed it up as it came through.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.30,1:31:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Different than another entity,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.30,1:31:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.30,1:31:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,like Master So-and-so on the other side
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.30,1:31:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,telling you to sell your sheep
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.30,1:32:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and buy goats or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.65,1:32:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Peter Ouspensky, Robert Schuller,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.68,1:32:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the founder of
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.68,1:32:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddhism, 510,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.68,1:32:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother Mira, 240.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.68,1:32:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another one of the Miras,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.68,1:32:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,mothers, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.93,1:32:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibetan masters can
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.93,1:32:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate from over 200
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.93,1:32:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.02,1:32:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We wondered where in the middle of all this
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.02,1:32:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and we got 220.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.02,1:32:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.10,1:32:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing of superhuman evolution,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.13,1:32:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but more a talent.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.13,1:32:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a talent.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.13,1:32:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Martin Buber, 405.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.18,1:32:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Thomas Aquinas, 435.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.18,1:32:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tertullian,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.18,1:32:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the greats of history,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.26,1:32:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,385.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.26,1:32:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Bonaventure, 385.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.47,1:32:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we get to some current people.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.47,1:32:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fitchinat Han, 460.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.47,1:32:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsongkhapa, 445.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.47,1:32:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This gives us a panorama
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.47,1:32:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of what exists on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.47,1:32:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of teachers are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.02,1:33:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How are they spread out
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.02,1:33:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,amongst the different religions?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.02,1:33:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's their exposure to the populace?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.21,1:33:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is their impact?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.50,1:33:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that somewhat defines
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.50,1:33:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or limits their impact on society.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.73,1:33:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now these are the ones
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.09,1:33:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that people really pester me with.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.09,1:33:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason I'm doing it
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.09,1:33:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is so they stop pestering me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.56,1:33:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.39,1:33:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to move over?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.39,1:33:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see from here?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.81,1:33:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.85,1:33:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we all knew that Yogananda
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.92,1:33:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,was in the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.92,1:33:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a saint, self-realized yoga,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.92,1:33:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and his famous book
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.14,1:33:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is an autobiography
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.14,1:33:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of a yoga.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.30,1:33:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Very famous and established
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.30,1:33:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in California
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.56,1:33:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and to this day has many followers
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.56,1:34:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and supporters.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.90,1:34:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lao Tzu, 520.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.90,1:34:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alan Watts, who popularized
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.90,1:34:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.93,1:34:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,himself was 485.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.93,1:34:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,John Blofield wrote
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.32,1:34:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,on Taoism, 465.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.32,1:34:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Silent Mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.32,1:34:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,465.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.06,1:34:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Poonja Ajit
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.06,1:34:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,wrote a book called
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.06,1:34:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing Happened, 520.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.06,1:34:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just trying to get a feel
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.06,1:34:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for the kind of writings
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.06,1:34:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and what kind of an energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.06,1:34:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,they're coming out of
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.06,1:34:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,which is always cultured by
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.06,1:34:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,ethnic, cultural, historic
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.18,1:34:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and other factors
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.18,1:34:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bernadette Roberts,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.42,1:34:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,445.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.69,1:34:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddha Nanda, Swami Buddha Nanda
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.69,1:34:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,who wrote the book
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.39,1:34:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind and its Control, 485.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.39,1:34:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Gene Klein
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.77,1:34:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is the more current Gene Klein.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.77,1:34:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ease of Being, 510.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.80,1:35:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chogyam Trungpa,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.80,1:35:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,495. Ram Dass, 425.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.80,1:35:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.06,1:35:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Leadbeater, 485.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.06,1:35:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Brad Shaw, who wrote, of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.06,1:35:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,all the famous books on recovery.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.18,1:35:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,M. Scott Peck
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.18,1:35:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,both way up in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.43,1:35:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Gangaji, I don't know who that is,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.43,1:35:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,475. Joseph Smith,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.43,1:35:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,510. He's certainly well known.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.43,1:35:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Emmet Fox, who is
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.43,1:35:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,extremely popular,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.43,1:35:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,especially with people who've been through
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.43,1:35:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,12-step groups, I think he was one of
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.43,1:35:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Wilson's favorites.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.43,1:35:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sermon on the Mount, 470.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.43,1:35:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thomas Merton,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.81,1:35:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,we used his book, New Seeds of
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.81,1:35:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Contemplation,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.81,1:35:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to calibrate from.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.81,1:35:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We get 510.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.81,1:35:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat Kahn, who is going to be speaking,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.81,1:35:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, either here or,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.18,1:35:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to be speaking, I'm going to be speaking with him
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.18,1:35:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,on the same platform, someplace.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.46,1:35:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Europe, someplace.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.46,1:35:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 499.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.46,1:35:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The next author I'm not familiar with,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.46,1:36:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Arjuna Ardha.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.81,1:36:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one that was sent to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.81,1:36:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Amachiyama, there's another mother, 300.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.81,1:36:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rudolf Steiner
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.35,1:36:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is interesting because
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.35,1:36:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it depends how you ask it
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.77,1:36:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and at what age you ask it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.77,1:36:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be 365, it could also be
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.77,1:36:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,475, and I think you remember
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.77,1:36:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Theosophy was 475.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.77,1:36:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, at his highest,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.13,1:36:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be his highest.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.13,1:36:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert Monroe, who wrote
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.18,1:36:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that fascinating book, Journeys Out of the Body,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.18,1:36:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I found him
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.09,1:36:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.81,1:36:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a voice that had a
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.81,1:36:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,peacefulness to it that was
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.14,1:36:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.50,1:36:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, he was
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.50,1:36:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,naive. Everybody knows
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.75,1:36:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the story of Monroe. How many
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.75,1:36:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,don't know it? Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.81,1:36:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Monroe was an engineer
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.81,1:36:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and suddenly at night he started
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.03,1:36:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,astral
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.03,1:36:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,projecting. He started going out of body
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.03,1:37:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and having these
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.22,1:37:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,adventures, exploring these astral domains.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.22,1:37:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd never heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.61,1:37:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't know how to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.61,1:37:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And he would wake up in his body
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.10,1:37:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,again. Sometimes he would have
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.10,1:37:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,amorous adventures, which he hoped his wife
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.10,1:37:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,did not notice.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.53,1:37:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet amorous entities
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.53,1:37:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in other domains.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.97,1:37:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Monroe, and he also went to some lower
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.97,1:37:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,astral domains, where
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.97,1:37:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,he had some unpleasant experiences.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.14,1:37:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And Monroe, being a scientist
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.14,1:37:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and an engineer by training,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.14,1:37:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,kept a careful notebook.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.14,1:37:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he would come back in the body, he would
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.14,1:37:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,turn on his overhead light, and he
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.14,1:37:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,would make careful notes of what his
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.14,1:37:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,experience was, and the atmospheric conditions,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.14,1:37:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the barometric pressure, the time
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.14,1:37:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of the month, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.23,1:37:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he didn't know what it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.27,1:37:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he kept a careful study of the
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.27,1:37:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,phenomena, and he was quite an
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.27,1:37:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,astrojector. I mean, he did a lot of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.39,1:37:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And got to explore a lot of astral realms.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.39,1:37:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And Monroe
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.84,1:38:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,wrote this book.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.84,1:38:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's charming about it
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.06,1:38:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is it's his complete naivete
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.06,1:38:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,as this all begins to happen to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.06,1:38:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He wrote Journeys
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.28,1:38:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the Body. Monroe then
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.28,1:38:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,devised the system of an altered
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.28,1:38:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.53,1:38:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He put on earphones, and there was a slight
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.53,1:38:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,difference in the frequency between the two
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.53,1:38:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,earphones. And the difference
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.64,1:38:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in the frequency would send you
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.64,1:38:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to different, older states of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.64,1:38:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Which, that plus intentionality
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.64,1:38:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and some self-hypnotic
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.64,1:38:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,techniques you could take off
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.64,1:38:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the body at will.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.22,1:38:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that was exciting. It was like a ten day
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.22,1:38:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,training they did in Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.22,1:38:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You spend ten days laying on your back on a
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.22,1:38:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,mattress with earphones on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.47,1:38:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And those that were
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.60,1:38:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,trained in it could agree on where they
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.60,1:38:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,were going to meet. And they would all leave the body
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.60,1:38:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,at the same time and meet out there, and then come back
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.60,1:38:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in the body. And
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.94,1:38:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, this is all ridiculous, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.94,1:38:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I went out of body, and then
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.94,1:39:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember when I
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.10,1:39:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,tried to come back in the body, I was upside down.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.10,1:39:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the body, and I'm
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.10,1:39:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,looking out the back of my head at the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.10,1:39:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I realized I had to back out,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.10,1:39:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,turn around 180, and go back in again.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.10,1:39:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that too strong?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.52,1:39:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I got turned back in correctly.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.52,1:39:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that was it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.84,1:39:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, you're out of the body. Of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.84,1:39:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it had happened to me spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.84,1:39:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Also,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.51,1:39:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,years before that, and so
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.51,1:39:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I had some familiarity with it
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.51,1:39:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,spontaneously, but I thought
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.51,1:39:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be interesting to study
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.51,1:39:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,how you could do it at will.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.40,1:39:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's true, you can explore many
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.40,1:39:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,domains.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.18,1:39:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Monroe had
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.18,1:39:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,in these earphones, he had
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.18,1:39:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,a little signal that you had to come back to the
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.18,1:39:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,body, because you could get lost in
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.18,1:39:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,adventures, and of course you're outside of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.18,1:40:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.18,1:40:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you get lost in various astral realms and all
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.18,1:40:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,kinds of adventures with other entities.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.18,1:40:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And so he had this whistle,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.18,1:40:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and he would blow that, and bang, you had to come back in the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.18,1:40:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like, you're trained to
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.18,1:40:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,like Bonzo returned to the dog
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.18,1:40:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,trainer, so you don't get lost
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.36,1:40:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in the woods chasing rabbits.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.38,1:40:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was Monroe, who is now
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.38,1:40:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,deceased, but that's a great classic.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.38,1:40:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.67,1:40:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kundalini energy is a great classic.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.67,1:40:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of those were sort of a classic.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.67,1:40:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.06,1:40:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,have other people
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.43,1:40:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.63,1:40:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eastern origin,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.63,1:40:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we come back to
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.63,1:40:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Father Pio, very well known,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.63,1:40:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.85,1:40:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,who also has difficulties, I think,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.85,1:40:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,with the church for some time.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.97,1:40:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And he also experienced
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.97,1:40:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,some very interesting
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.97,1:40:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,things, such as by
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.97,1:40:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,location, in which his spirit
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.97,1:40:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,could split and be in two places
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.97,1:41:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.21,1:41:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard Buck was one of the most famous
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.21,1:41:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,authors of people who are studying
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.21,1:41:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness and enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.21,1:41:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a physician who
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.21,1:41:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,became enlightened and went into
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.21,1:41:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a state of cosmic consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.21,1:41:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and wrote the classic.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.21,1:41:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a classic book called
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.21,1:41:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Cosmic Consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.21,1:41:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Physicians were not exactly
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.21,1:41:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the kind of people who
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.21,1:41:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,championed such concepts,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.21,1:41:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so he was rather courageous in that
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.21,1:41:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as a practicing physician,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.34,1:41:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,he explained his own
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.34,1:41:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,subjective experiences.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.90,1:41:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And Raymond Moody, who has written
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.90,1:41:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,much about near-death experiences
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.90,1:41:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and death and dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.90,1:41:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Anthroposophy is 405.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.90,1:41:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nathaniel Brandon is Psychology
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.90,1:41:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and Self-Esteem.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.06,1:41:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really Ayn Rand's Objectivism,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.06,1:41:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't it? Objectivism by Ayn Rand
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.13,1:41:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.38,1:41:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,400s.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.02,1:41:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, now we've got some
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.02,1:42:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,crooked people here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.02,1:42:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the pathway
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.34,1:42:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of inner light and sound.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.81,1:42:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,315.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.85,1:42:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,C.S. Lewis, 390.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.10,1:42:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightworkers. Ron Sedona,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.10,1:42:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of people that are lightworkers.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.10,1:42:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As a group,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.10,1:42:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,there are 215.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.10,1:42:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sri Siva,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.86,1:42:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sri Guruji, 220.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.69,1:42:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sri Swami Master Ram.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.69,1:42:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see there's many
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.14,1:42:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,teachers with these exotic names.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.14,1:42:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.97,1:42:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the thing is not to be
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.97,1:42:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,misled by the ethnic novelty
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.97,1:42:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.14,1:42:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the novelty of the name
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.23,1:42:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,or the title.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.43,1:42:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's important is what they calibrate at.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.43,1:42:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to have a
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.31,1:42:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,neighbor down the street teaching you
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.31,1:42:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,who's at 480
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.31,1:42:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,than a Swami something-rather who's at 220.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.31,1:43:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand? It just lacks
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.31,1:43:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the glamour, but it's
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.31,1:43:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.60,1:43:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there are various other things of great interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.60,1:43:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Siddha Yoga,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.10,1:43:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,395. Joseph
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.10,1:43:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Campbell, who's a well-known writer, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.10,1:43:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,410. And we've got Nostradamus
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.10,1:43:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,again. Then there's various things like
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.10,1:43:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,websites. People send me these things.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.10,1:43:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're, again,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.39,1:43:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,quite impressive looking.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.39,1:43:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, this fancy readout.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.72,1:43:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,220.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.77,1:43:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ashram of Enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.77,1:43:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Advaita,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.40,1:43:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Modism, Vedanta.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.40,1:43:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So a lot of these teachers, I just put them here
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.40,1:43:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,because people sent them to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.40,1:43:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mountain Order of Sri Shankar
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.53,1:43:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,something-rather, 305.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.53,1:43:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So people send me all these
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.14,1:43:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,things and therefore you'll have to punish
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.14,1:43:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,them. Don't punish me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.81,1:44:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakuya,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.11,1:44:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Taizan, Maizumi for
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.11,1:44:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,a 505. These are some Zen teachers.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.11,1:44:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen teachers
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.38,1:44:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and masters who write books about
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.38,1:44:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen are very often
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.38,1:44:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in 500s.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.40,1:44:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bernie Glassman Roshi was
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.40,1:44:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,455 on Zen practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.40,1:44:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,465. This is
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.81,1:44:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,White Plum Asanga is
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.81,1:44:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a group, Zen
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.81,1:44:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabbalah
